{"tid":1248700,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Be Water 小心尾班車後d狗暴力清場","createTime":"2019-06-21T13:56:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-21T17:18:28.000Z","uid":150625,"like":47,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e2469ade6d2bb07b56c5f15bd31ffbd03567ddf8","tid":1248700,"uid":150625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T13:56:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">只係要大家小心!!! 絕對唔係要大家散!!!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n警犬又玩橋唔怕舊 最緊要有用<br />\n已經有多個po肯定狗屋以外有做部處<br />\n警犬可能再次等<span style=\"color: red;\">尾班車後</span>又無理用過份暴力驅散 包括<span style=\"color: red;\">催淚彈</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">狗屋d狗可能同時衝出黎夾擊</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">以軍器廠街既地勢好可能會引起嚴重意外</span></span><br />\n呢方面大家一定要<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">保持冷靜<br />\n互相信任 尤其係信任撲煙隊等<br />\n唔好慌亂走避</span></span>以免自己同其他人受傷<br />\n若真係情勢嚴峻<br />\n一定要及時be water 冷靜向金鐘烈士祭祀現場後退會合其他群眾<br />\n亦要<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">記得救人</span></span>唔好比同伴捉入狗屋"},{"pid":"78d06a1bb6f12a7bb3e2e0448e2cbdce06004c29","tid":1248700,"uid":150625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T13:56:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35251800353c70c730a9236672aa9b63712ab1df","tid":1248700,"uid":150625,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T13:57:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0809435ebb10ef0502af62638ecb4609a91f080e","tid":1248700,"uid":150625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T13:57:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e270c521acf2c78a88b8e699bd4e11d917b85e6","tid":1248700,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T13:58:18.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4b67ab06ea10f2101130